---
title: "Careers Stay up to date"
---

<div class="page-description__title-container career-up-to-date__wrapper">
    <div class="container">
        <img class="career-up-to-date__top-image" src="/img/career_signup.svg" alt="" />

        <h2 class="page-description__title career-up-to-date__title">
            Stay up-to-date with our latest job offers
        </h2>
        <div class="page-description__sub-title career-up-to-date__sub-title">
            Sign up for our job posting alerts, and heaps of opportunities<br />
            will come knocking on your door.
        </div>
        <div class="yellow-divider page-description__yellow-underline">
        </div>
        <div class="page-description__description career-up-to-date__description">
            <p>
                A voucher of <strong>1.000.000VND</strong> from Phuc Anh Tech Store will also be given<br />
                to one lucky submissions each month!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form id="careerSignupForm" action="/Static/data/careers.json">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
                    <input class="career-input" type="text" id="submission-name" name="name" placeholder="YOUR NAME" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
                    <input class="career-input" type="email" id="submission-email" name="email" placeholder="YOUR EMAIL" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
                    <button class="career-button" type="submit">Sign me up now</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="careerSignupDialog" class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__container">
        <div class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__content">
            <img class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__icon" alt="" src="/img/career_tick_icon.png"/>
            <h3 class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__title">Sign-up successful!</h3>
            <div class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__description">
                <p>
                    You will be the first to know about our job postings. Also, you now stand a chance to win a 1.000.000VND voucher.<br />
                    For more information on the job alerts, the prize and the past winners, please see <a href="#">Our Facebook page</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <span id="careerSignupCloseButton" class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__button-close">Close</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="careerSignupDialogEmail" class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__container">
        <div class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__content">
            <img class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__icon" alt="" src="/img/career_smile_icon.png" />
            <h3 class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__title">Your email address is already signed up!</h3>
            <div class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__description career-up-to-date__success-dialog__description-duplicated-email">
                <p>
                    We'll keep you updated with our latest job postings.<br/>
                    For more information on the job alerts, the prize and the past winners, please see <a href="#">Our Facebook page</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <span id="careerSignupCloseButtonEmail" class="career-up-to-date__success-dialog__button-close">Close</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>